precis:
Authority to enter into CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS with the provinces,
territories, municipalities, First Nations, private entreprises, etc., for
the purposes of making improvements at border crossings and undertaking
transportation planning and modal integration initiatives under the
National System Integration Component of the STRATEGIC HIGHWAY
INFRASTRUCTURE PROGRAM.
